  "note": "Curated synthetic tool-use task set for eval-v2 ruler. Author-written, public-safe. Does NOT derive from any customer traffic. Each task defines a tool schema and a prompt that requires a specific tool call. Used to score G1 (tool-call validity), G2 (correct tool selection + valid args), G3 (latency), G4 (cost efficiency).",
  "tasks": [
